known as a paradox, my friend.

41
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:17,750
The closer you get to the truth,
the further away you'll get from me.

42
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,600
From who I was.

43
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,940
